ctor_2.13, such as classic ActorSystem, Props, ActorRef, dispatch, serialization, configuration, and DNS utilities. If tests continue to exercise DNS internals that touch sun.net.dns, preserve the existing JVM/native-image module export flag --add-exports=java.base/sun.net.dns=ALL-UNNAMED.\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"Pekko 2.0.0-M1 is a milestone and is not source-compatible with all 1.x APIs, so more deprecated 1.x test targets may need replacement rather than setup.\",\n    \"Pekko documentation recommends pekko-testkit for application-level actor testing, but it is not required to exercise the core pekko-actor artifact and should not be added unless local Gradle verification proves it is necessary.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0429804a3d107e5d016a406a50706c81938c5984e289c59904\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1411, "output": 1247, "cacheRead": 30208, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 32866, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782606404170, "responseId": "resp_0429804a3d107e5d016a406a449b948193b42627ce01bee032"}}
